            </h3>
        </div>
        <div class="col"></div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="container mb-5">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md bg-light shadow rounded">
            <div class="container p-5">
                <h2>'$100 Ramen' and Michelin Stars - Food Is at the Center of Japan's Tourism Resurgence</h2>
