                    <p>Japan—a food destination—is saturated with sushi counters, izakaya watering holes, prix-fixe kaiseki, and family-run Shokudo, among other types of eateries...</p>
                </a>
                
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md mx-4 bg-light shadow rounded">
            <div class="container p-5">
                <h2>'Dr. Beach' names the top 10 US beaches for 2023</h2>
                <a class="link-dark" href="https://www.cnn.com/travel/best-us-beaches-2023-dr-beach/index.html" target="_blank">
                    <p>Half of the top 10 beaches in the United States for 2023 are in Florida and Hawaii. That’s according to the 2023 list of best US beaches released in May by “Dr. Beach,” aka coastal scientist Stephen Leatherman...</p>
